\v 18 \x + \xo 5:18: a \xt Deu 25:4; 1Cor 9:9; \xo b \xt Mat 10:10; Luk 10:7.\x*becauseВҰ138044 the scripturesВҰ138046 say, вҖңDon't muzzleВҰ138050 the ox working on the threshingВҰ138048 floor,вҖқ andВҰ138053 вҖңA workerВҰ138056 deserves their wages.вҖқ
